products.shortDescription: When a commercial property opportunity is recognised and finance is needed, Nedbank Corporate Property Finance leads the market in providing agile solutions that help realise your vision. Nedbank Corporate Property Finance specialises in financing commercial, industrial, retail and residential development property, offering loan funding to developers, owners, occupiers and investors. Agile financial solutions include access to undrawn funds, interest-only periods, fixed and floating interest rates, flexible repayments and residual value transactions.
